definitions.definition: A town in the borough of Richmond upon Thames , south-western Greater London , England , historically in Middlesex ( OS grid ref TQ1673 ) .
Twickenham Stadium , the largest rugby stadium in England.
An unincorporated community in Wheeler County , Oregon , United States .
